**Bitcoin Sportsbook** was a site that is used for parimutuel wagering on sporting events and Bitcoin-related metrics such as the BTC/USD exchange rate at a future date.

##History

The site went offline after a period of inactivity (2.1).

This service was not related to similarly named [[BTCSportsBet]] or another service named BTC SportsBetting.

